01:18:12,000 --> 01:18:14,060
It's that the potential amount of information

1988
01:18:14,060 --> 01:18:15,920
is infinite in a black hole.

1989
01:18:16,180 --> 01:18:18,340
It's quantum mechanics which keeps it

1990
01:18:18,340 --> 01:18:19,180
from being infinite

1991
01:18:19,560 --> 01:18:21,120
and gives you a finite entropy.

1992
01:18:21,760 --> 01:18:22,520
All right,

1993
01:18:22,520 --> 01:18:24,120
so that's the origin of entropy

1994
01:18:24,120 --> 01:18:25,420
in black hole physics.

1995
01:18:26,120 --> 01:18:27,500
Let's talk about temperature.

1996
01:18:28,580 --> 01:18:30,060
We could do this in two ways.

1997
01:18:31,360 --> 01:18:33,020
