1998
01:18:33,360 --> 01:18:35,300
Here we have the entropy written

1999
01:18:35,300 --> 01:18:36,380
in terms of the area.

2000
01:18:36,640 --> 01:18:39,100
The area can be written in terms of the radius,

2001
01:18:39,360 --> 01:18:40,620
and the radius can be

2002
01:18:40,620 --> 01:18:41,880
written in terms of the mass,

2003
01:18:42,180 --> 01:18:43,470
and the mass can be

2004
01:18:43,470 --> 01:18:44,760
written in terms of the energy.

2005
01:18:45,340 --> 01:18:46,420
So in principle,

2006
01:18:46,420 --> 01:18:47,820
we have a connection

2007
01:18:47,820 --> 01:18:50,800
between entropy and energy.

2008
01:18:52,120 --> 01:18:53,320
When we know the connection

2009
01:18:53,320 --> 01:18:54,880
between entropy and energy,

2010
01:18:55,120 --> 01:18:57,020
