2011
01:18:57,240 --> 01:18:59,220
dE equals T dS.

2012
01:18:59,460 --> 01:19:01,340
But we can short-circuit this.

2013
01:19:01,640 --> 01:19:05,640
We can also say that the definition of temperature,

2014
01:19:05,900 --> 01:19:08,640
when you write dE equals T dS,

2015
01:19:10,759 --> 01:19:13,240
basically this says that the definition

2016
01:19:13,240 --> 01:19:16,180
of the temperature is the change in energy

2017
01:19:16,180 --> 01:19:18,780
when you change S by one unit.

2018
01:19:19,520 --> 01:19:22,480
If dS is just one unit of entropy,

2019
01:19:22,480 --> 01:19:23,880
we can write approximate.

2020
01:19:24,360 --> 01:19:27,260
dE equals T dS.

2021
01:19:27,740 --> 01:19:30,180
And if we change the entropy by one unit,

2022
01:19:30,340 --> 01:19:33,820
then the temperature is just the change in the entropy.

2023
01:19:34,160 --> 01:19:34,680
Sorry,

2024
01:19:34,680 --> 01:19:36,000
the change in the energy.

