01:25:36,100 --> 01:25:39,320
We haven't done anything about black body radiation yet.

2190
01:25:39,440 --> 01:25:41,440
You stand far away from the black hole.

2191
01:25:41,560 --> 01:25:43,060
It's exactly the same as the sun.

2192
01:25:43,540 --> 01:25:46,540
