01:26:17,420 --> 01:26:18,680
The energy of a photon

2206
01:26:18,700 --> 01:26:20,820
when it climbs up out of

2207
01:26:20,820 --> 01:26:22,940
the gravitational field of the sun

2208
01:26:23,460 --> 01:26:25,320
