2211
01:26:31,500 --> 01:26:34,100
than the energy that we might have ascribed to it

2212
01:26:34,100 --> 01:26:36,200
if we stood right at the surface of the sun.

2213
01:26:36,680 --> 01:26:39,180
When we do the thermodynamics of the sun

