01:27:32,860 --> 01:27:35,060
near the surface of the sun.

2240
01:27:35,760 --> 01:27:39,080
So this is the correct temperature to ascribe

2241
01:27:39,080 --> 01:27:42,240
to somebody observing the sun from far away.

2242
01:27:45,299 --> 01:27:47,040
So would the...

